### *Find Multiple*

This call retrieves all images of an organization based on the requested image ID(s).

__To search multiple image IDs, enter each ID into the JSON array "imageIds"__ 

```JSON
{
    "imageIds": [
        {
            "id": "imageID1"
        },
        {
            "id": "imageID2"
        },
        {
            "id": "imageID3"
        }
    ]
}
```

