### *Transform Image Metadata*

This call transforms and retrieves details of all transformed images based on the requirements in the request.

__To transform multiple images, enter each ID into the JSON array "imageIds"__ 

```JSON
{
    "imageIds": [
        {
            "id": "id1"
        },
        {
            "id": "id2"
        },
        {
            "id": "id3"
        }
    ],
    "quality": int,
    "width": int,
    "height": int,
    "fitMode": [
         "COVER",
         "BOUNDS",
         "CROP",
     ]
}
